<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>陕西秦麒鑫盛能源进出口有限责任公司 | Shaanxi Qinqi Xinsheng Energy Import and Export Co., Ltd.</title>
<style>
  *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
  body{font-family:Arial,"Microsoft YaHei",sans-serif;background:url("bg_background.jpg") center center / cover no-repeat fixed;padding:20px}
  .content{max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto}
  .title{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.95);text-align:center;padding:25px;border-radius:10px;margin-bottom:20px}
  .title h1{font-size:24px;color:#222;margin-bottom:8px}
  .title h2{font-size:18px;color:#444;font-weight:normal}
  .item{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.93);padding:20px;border-radius:10px;margin:20px 0}
  .item h2{font-size:20px;color:#222;margin-bottom:5px}
  .item h3{font-size:16px;color:#555;font-weight:normal;margin-bottom:15px}
  .item img{width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:6px;display:block}
  .contact{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.95);padding:25px;border-radius:10px;text-align:center;font-size:18px;margin-top:20px}
  .contact a{color:#1a4d8c;text-decoration:none}
  .contact a:hover{text-decoration:underline}
  .contact .en{font-size:16px;color:#555;margin-top:3px;display:block}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="content">
  <div class="title">
    <h1>陕西秦麒鑫盛能源进出口有限责任公司</h1>
    <h2>Shaanxi Qinqi Xinsheng Energy Import and Export Co., Ltd.</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="item">
    <h2>公司门头</h2><h3>Company Entrance</h3>
    < img src="entrance.jpg" alt="公司门头 / Company Entrance">
  </div>
  <div class="item">
    <h2>车间场景</h2><h3>Workshop Scene</h3>
    < img src="workshop.jpg" alt="车间场景 / Workshop Scene">
  </div>
  <div class="item">
    <h2>生产场景</h2><h3>Production Scene</h3>
    < img src="production.jpg" alt="生产场景 / Production Scene">
  </div>
  <div class="item">
    <h2>仓库展示</h2><h3>Warehouse Display</h3>
    < img src="warehouse.jpg" alt="仓库展示 / Warehouse Display">
  </div>
  <div class="contact">
    联系电话：+86 177 0926 9768<span class="en">Contact Number</span><br>
    WhatsApp：<span class="en">WhatsApp</span><br>
    邮箱：<span class="en">Email</span>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
